snippet.textDisplay: I too am a paranoid parents. It's why all three of my children still sleep in my room. They're all really young; 3yrs old, 2yrs old, and 5 months old so them sleeping in my room isnt "weird". My 4 cats also sleep in our room. Theres been so many times that I dragged myself out of bed at ungodly hours cos I couldnt hear one of my cats and afraid they were stuck and suffocating (happened to my first kitten in a drawer. He lived, but most likely only because I've always been obsessive about where my cats are and heard him right away. My antique dresser drawer was ruined that day, literally ripped apart. But kitty was okay and that's all that mattered.
